extends layout

block content
  nav.navbar.navbar-inverse.navbar-fixed-top(role='navigation')
    .container
      .navbar-header
        button.navbar-toggle(type='button', data-toggle='collapse', data-target='#bs-example-navbar-collapse-1')
          span.sr-only Toggle navigation
          span.icon-bar
          span.icon-bar
          span.icon-bar
        a.navbar-brand(href='/')
          img(src="/img/logo_white_exp.png", style="display: inline; height: 50px;")
      #bs-example-navbar-collapse-1.collapse.navbar-collapse
        ul.nav.navbar-nav.navbar-right
          li
            a(href='#home') HOME
          li
            a(href='#product') PRODUCT
          li
            a(href='#specifications') SPECIFICATIONS
  header#home.carousel.slide
    ol.carousel-indicators
      li.active(data-target='#home', data-slide-to='0')
      li(data-target='#home', data-slide-to='1')
      li(data-target='#home', data-slide-to='2')
      li(data-target='#home', data-slide-to='3')
    .carousel-inner
      .item.active
        .fill(style="background-image:url('/img/banner_0.jpg');")
      .item
        .fill(style="background-image:url('/img/banner_1.jpg');")
      .item
        .fill(style="background-image:url('/img/banner_2.jpg');")
      .item
        .fill(style="background-image:url('/img/banner_3.jpg');")
    a.left.carousel-control(href='#home', data-slide='prev')
      span.icon-prev
    a.right.carousel-control(href='#home', data-slide='next')
      span.icon-next
  section
    .row
      .col-md-5.col-md-offset-1
        h2.page-header Why?
        p 
          | We believe living in a technology driven time, there is a need for a compact multi-tool which fulfills the desire for power supply, lighting and speakers. A stylish, yet durable product offers a solution to the problem which particularly arises when people engage in outdoor activities such as camping, attending festivals or having picnic with the friends.
      .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        img.img-responsive(src='/img/addy_why.jpg', alt='')
  section(style="background-color: #dfdfdf;")
    .row
      .col-md-12.col-md-offset-1
        h2.page-header What?
      .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        img.img-responsive(src='/img/addy_what.png', alt='')
      .col-md-5.col-md-offset-1
        p 
          | ADDY is a modular and multifunctional power station for active people who like to spend time outdoor. It's made by a long lasting battery and three layers which provide light, sound and charging facilities. ADDY is portable, durable and customizable for all your activities away from electrical sources. The design of this product is captivating at the first sight for the clean shape and the high quality materials.
        p
          | As far as there are many different way for spending time outdoor, every user could choose different layers depending on his needs.
        p
          | You can connect with ADDY through (micro)-USB, aux, WIFI and Bluetooth. On your smartphone you can download an app on which you can control all the functions such as light color, battery usage and music playback.
        p
          | Strong performances, modular customization and simple design make ADDY not just a piece of equipment, but a multifunctional companion you can always rely on.
  section#specifications
    .row
      .col-md-11.col-md-offset-1
        h1.page-header
          | Product Specifications
      .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            h4
              i.fa.fa-fw.fa-database
              |  Base Layer
          .panel-body
            ul
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Powerbank
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Lithium ion, 6000mAh
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | 2 USB ports
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Bluetouth, 3.5mm stereo
      .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            h4
              i.fa.fa-fw.fa-plug
              |  Battery Layer
          .panel-body
            ul
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Lithium ion, 2400mAh
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | USB port
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | extra charge
    .row  
      .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            h4
              i.fa.fa-fw.fa-music
              |  Speaker Layer
          .panel-body
            ul
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Full-range listening
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Wireless and ultra-compact
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | up to 7h of playback time
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | 30hz-28khz frequency range
      .col-md-4.col-md-offset-1
        .panel.panel-default
          .panel-heading
            h4
              i.fa.fa-fw.fa-lightbulb-o
              |  Lighting Layer
          .panel-body
            ul
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Ambient light
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Low power LED
              li
                i.fa.fa-fw.fa-check
                | Changeable light color
  section#product(style="background-color: #dfdfdf;")
    .row
      .col-md-3.col-md-offset-2
        img(src="/img/addy_0.png")
        img(ng-src="{{thirdLayer.img}}")
        img(ng-src="{{secondLayer.img}}")
        img(ng-src="{{firstLayer.img}}")
        img(src="/img/addy_4.png")
      .col-md-3
        h1 Customize
        select(ng-model="thirdLayer" ng-options="layer.name for layer in layers track by layer.name", ng-change="changeLayer(11)")
          option(value="") select 3rd layer
        select(ng-model="secondLayer" ng-options="layer.name for layer in layers track by layer.name", ng-change="changeLayer(11)")
          option(value="") select 2nd layer
        select(ng-model="firstLayer" ng-options="layer.name for layer in layers track by layer.name", ng-change="changeLayer(11)")
          option(value="") select 1st layer
      .col-md-3
        h1 Total Price
        h2 €{{ totalPrice }}
        button.btn.btn-success.btn-lg Order
  footer
    .row
      .col-md-11
        p Copyright © Addy 2015